"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>HTML <code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code> 요소</strong>는 표의 열을 묶는 그룹을 정의합니다.</span></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"655\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/colgroup.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples </a> and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">콘텐츠 카테고리</a></th>\n   <td>없음.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 콘텐츠</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup#attr-span\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>span</code></a> 특성이 존재하는 경우 없음. <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Empty_element\">빈 요소</a>입니다.<br>\n    그렇지 않은 경우 0개 이상의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/col\"><code>&lt;col&gt;</code></a> 요소.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">태그 생략</th>\n   <td>첫 번째 자식이 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/col\"><code>&lt;col&gt;</code></a> 요소이며, 바로 앞의 요소가 닫는 태그를 생략한 <code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code> 요소가 아닐 때, 여는 태그를 생략할 수 있습니다.<br>\n    바로 뒤에 스페이스나 주석이 오지 않으면 닫는 태그를 생략할 수 있습니다.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 부모 요소</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a> 요소. <code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code>은 모든 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a> 요소 앞에 위치해야 하며, <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> 안에 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/caption\"><code>&lt;caption&gt;</code></a> 요소가 존재하는 경우 <code>&lt;caption&gt;</code> 뒤에 와야 합니다.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 ARIA 역할</th>\n   <td>없음</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM 인터페이스</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"특성","title":"특성","isH3":false,"content":"<p>이 요소는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">전역 특성</a>을 포함합니다.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"bgcolor\"><a id=\"attr-bgcolor\" href=\"#attr-bgcolor\"><b><code>bgcolor</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>열 그룹의 배경색. '#' 문자로 시작하는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#rgb_색상\">6자리 16진수 RGB 코드</a> 또는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#색상_키워드\">사전 정의된 색상 키워드</a>를 사용할 수 있습니다.\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>참고:</strong> 표준 특성이 아니므로 사용하지 마세요. 배경색을 적용하려면 CSS <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> 특성을 사용해야 합니다.</div>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"span\"><a id=\"attr-span\" href=\"#attr-span\"><b><code>span</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd><code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code>이 차지할 열의 수를 나타내는 양의 정수. 기본값은 1입니다. 내부에 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/col\"><code>&lt;col&gt;</code></a> 요소가 존재하면 사용할 수 없습니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code> 요소의 예제는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a> 요소 문서에서 볼 수 있습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/tables.html#the-colgroup-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.colgroup"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.colgroup","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"특성","id":"특성"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"specifications"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"}],"summary":"HTML <colgroup> 요소는 표의 열을 묶는 그룹을 정의합니다.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<colgroup>: The Table Column Group element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"colgroup","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<colgroup> : l'élément regroupant des colonnes","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<colgroup>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<colgroup>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/html/element/colgroup","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/html/element/colgroup/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Hypertext Markup Language"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 요소 참고서"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup","title":"<colgroup>"}],"pageTitle":"<colgroup> - HTML: Hypertext Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}